imdb.plot outline: Rita Villon is the wealthy heiress of the most successful perfume company in the country, Senorita Scents. She is an absessive- compulsive perfectionist feared by all of her employees for being a strict boss. Despite her wealth, Rita never had a boyfriend and has no interest in men but deep inside, she long for love and affection expectedly from her family.In a twist of events, Rita loses all her wealth. On her way to gaining back all the things she lost, she stumbes upon five orphaned children: Kyla, Charisse, Apol, Rambo and Girlie who will help her get back on her feet. Along their journey, Rita develops affection for the children who will teach her the true value of happiness.
